comments: Kispert (WAS) and Williams (CHI) mutually engage and immediately disengage as marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Kispert (WAS) and DeRozan (CHI) engage in marginal arm to arm contact during the rebound.
Porzingis (WAS) initiates contact with DeRozan's (CHI) right arm after the start of his upward shooting motion, which alters his driving shot attempt.
Vucevic (CHI) establishes himself in Avdija's (WAS) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Williams (CHI) brings his arm toward Morris' (WAS) path and marginal contact occurs during the drive.
LaVine (CHI) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently exiting.
DeRozan (CHI) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently exiting.
Caruso (CHI) initiates body contact with Porzingis (WAS) and dislodges him from his position.
Avdija (WAS) maintains a legal guarding position and incidental contact occurs as he defends DeRozan (CHI) during the drive.
Williams (CHI) and Porzingis (WAS) engage in marginal arm to arm contact during the rebound.
Vucevic (CHI) and Kuzma (WAS) pursue the loose ball and marginal arm contact occurs.
Porzingis (WAS) cleanly deflects DeRozan's (CHI) pass.
Kuzma (WAS) gathers the pass with both hands on his right foot and takes one step before releasing his shot attempt at the basket.
LaVine (CHI) is imminently exiting the lane within three seconds.
Avdija (WAS) moves alongside LaVine's (CHI) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Morris (WAS) commits a take foul on DeRozan (CHI).
Caruso (CHI) is in the paint for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Caruso (CHI) releases the in-bound pass within five seconds.
Morris (WAS) wraps Vucevic's (CHI) opposite-side hip and affects his FOM.
Kuzma (WAS) commits a take foul on LaVine (CHI).
